rch\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ig.ft.com/sites/business-book-award/books/2019/shortlist/the-age-of-surveillance-capitalism-by-shoshana-zuboff/|title=The Age of Surveillance Capitalism by Shoshana Zuboff|last=Graphics|first=FT Interactive|website=FT Business book of the year award|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-01-16}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Age of Surveillance Capitalism, The}}\n[[Category:American non-fiction books]]\n[[Category:2018 non-fiction books]]\n[[Category:Books critical of capitalism]]\n", "name_user": "Skanye11", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200ePremise:hope you do not mind, just wanted to expand further on Zuboffs concept surrounding Surveillance Capitalism.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Age_of_Surveillance_Capitalism"}
